# --- secrets: never commit ---
bot/secrets.json
**/playwright_cookies.json
**/*cookies*.json
.env
*.env

# --- large third-party raw bulk downloads ---
# Regeneratable via data/external/transfermarkt/extract_relevant.py and
# data/external/odds/extract_international_odds.py against a fresh public download.
# The small, already-filtered outputs those scripts produce ARE committed:
#   data/external/transfermarkt/extracted/*.csv
#   data/external/odds/international_fixture_odds.csv
data/external/transfermarkt/transfermarkt-datasets/
data/external/odds/fixtures.csv
data/external/odds/odds.csv
# StatsBomb open-data: full raw mirror (immutable, several GB). Re-cloneable via
# `git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/statsbomb/open-data`. Never edited in place.
data/external/statsbomb/open-data/

